sub_title: MSc Biology and Education student at Leiden University
summary:
Currently following the Biology and Education MSc at Leiden University.
As a student of biology, my interests mainly lie in the history of the human lineage, as well the mechanisms behind evolution. For extracurricular activities, I have been involved in varied committe work ranging from leisurely activities to large, educational & career-oriented events.
